ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"你果個係咪無底mousse 圈嚟&hellip;&hellip;唔係蛋糕模?"},{"pid":"4dbaff67deb43c8d61ba0d4a2299ac44a5a492a2","tid":115054,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:32:43.000Z","msg":"小學生都整得好過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8391e45edb14754a5f9fd7b6868859652de88038","tid":115054,"uid":48195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"擺明要用錫紙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你個圈無底？一係爛<br />\n焗到流哂出黎知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492c879fcce68fdd91af262f9ec8dd802d9683a6","tid":115054,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:34:53.000Z","msg":"你個模無底架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用返蛋糕模，蛋白打起要打到反轉碗唔跌落嚟<br />\n唔洗包錫紙"},{"pid":"60866f28cad3085ffbf3191e49bd3c254ecc39a3","tid":115054,"uid":39876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"心思最重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcba0306bc1bd8418ce133c9c56731ecdba6cddd","tid":115054,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"買蛋糕模"},{"pid":"8e2ceb67ddf31e228a7911f938865d383028aee8","tid":115054,"uid":55391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你果個係咪無底mousse 圈嚟&hellip;&hellip;唔係蛋糕模?</blockquote><br />\n我望咗陣先睇得明<br />\n一開始以為樓主係整蛋糕底再cup個圓形<br />\n原來係就咁圓形模漏晒出嚟？<br />\n<br />\n用呢d薄嘅圓形模唔係唔得，但要用牛油紙紮實個底，再倒d麵糊落去，咁焗先唔會漏，先會焗得起<br />\ngoogle唔到圖，類似係牛油紙放底，上面放個圓形模，然後突出嘅牛油紙要捲實成個模嘅邊邊，形成一條牛油紙圈圍住個圓模底外圍咁，再倒d麵糊入去焗"},{"pid":"b9d2932b1cc7b732b02eab4b243e9a495081a7bb","tid":115054,"uid":83934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:39:57.000Z","msg":"你個模無底？"},{"pid":"7c86e0723054cf47668bca5f718ccc92a0aa8b7e","tid":115054,"uid":55205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二個係做乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我整完第一個之後 <br />\n我fd話其實唔使用錫紙包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果唔用既你咪用有底托嗰個囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你個盤又唔平 啲蛋糕漿咪順住啲隙縫漏出嚟"},{"pid":"58de568bc757b3b5e7904170e041fabeb35abb5a","tid":115054,"uid":14524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T10:44:42.000Z","msg":"我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa797b4b5b1a1615a1ea563b2537c812f25057de","tid":115054,"uid":28196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/10/185733_c42ff199f913af68bdb353af480ab4e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F10%2F185733_c42ff199f913af68bdb353af480ab4e2.jpg&h=e8f1e0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用牛油紙圍住個模摺成大約咁樣<br />\n<br />\n用正常蛋糕模的話，cut好同模相約size既圓形牛油紙放模底，再加一條長條型牛油紙圍邊就可以<br />\n祝下次成功<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c1b6b8285f44fd868d504c16d51045a00b0ef5","tid":115054,"uid":33292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:09:21.000Z","msg":"有機會爐火太猛 同埋蛋糕要落蛋糕模 仲有你個蛋糕打唔起 睇到個蛋糕太實 正常焗完會高少少"},{"pid":"b39b12245669ee1d96822d2ac4a85098b22c97be","tid":115054,"uid":70399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T11:19:06.000Z","msg":"Sorry我見到第二個笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你整比女朋友？<br />\n其實cut反個形出黎<br />\n加小小野上去可以併個卡通人物出黎"},{"pid":"500a193ce56b2dec18462c188a2bb21a6108ad77","tid":115054,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好玩唔玩玩屎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d596a32a01e9f4aafb6ed3d6e494e60f5793469a","tid":115054,"uid":900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好玩唔玩玩屎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbda0db89fe87c47fb0be16c062f9d03d32c656","tid":115054,"uid":32623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"收手啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf71e16be9f3bfc53748104b47a2a2ea08fa750","tid":115054,"uid":34948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"ig女神？"},{"pid":"d05a73163154698d6ede66a1421a7c4ff9541594","tid":115054,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:16:04.000Z","msg":"點解會漏到成個焗盤都係"},{"pid":"23ea4b10b7f95e71247036a238eeb0da697e4793","tid":115054,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第二個係做乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我整完第一個之後 <br />\n我fd話其實唔使用錫紙包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常個模有底就唔洗錫紙"},{"pid":"13067231d135c75b4aeb6d7974d92f3b7afb0239","tid":115054,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"認真答你~~<br />\n1.包得唔實~<br />\n2.爐溫過高~<br />\n<br />\n解決方法<br />\n1.唔撚害人la!<br />\n2.怕唔實就包多層,爐溫慢慢試((個個爐唔同)"},{"pid":"991d4429890c94f642e042e92ccccd7eb1bba387","tid":115054,"uid":23701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:25:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>第二個係做乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我整完第一個之後 <br />\n我fd話其實唔使用錫紙包住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正常個模有底就唔洗錫紙</blockquote><br />\n梗係唔係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係唔係搞笑 唔用錫紙<br />\n樓主連份量，分分鐘個模都用錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬呀，唔好搵自己男/女朋友較飛啦"},{"pid":"a90e64c0beecc6e3a8bd134adf8288b432e9f975","tid":115054,"uid":83849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:28:08.000Z","msg":"第2個流晒出來咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38bf1cc0bbeb348cb72e68fa4dbd1d6c4a57362","tid":115054,"uid":28372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:28:25.000Z","msg":"可能太乾 可以隔離放碗水一齊焗"},{"pid":"30baa85c8d1560ef5f2a15b84b807b9d85b17a69","tid":115054,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:28:55.000Z","msg":"都係睇唔過眼~巴打不如用入爐既紙杯仔整~~7分滿就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係果句LA~起碼有得食~發得樣衰既就飛左個頂加D裝飾~唔食得都睇得丫!!"},{"pid":"b26ec38866cad3f559644120f136dd2a7e026f54","tid":115054,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋第一個其實算成功!不過係太早脫模!!<br />\n應該成個倒轉佢等佢凍小小先甩模!!咁樣就唔會太塔!!"},{"pid":"33ed4f0bcab5b9f538354648849fddafae6f6425","tid":115054,"uid":14616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:37:53.000Z","msg":"你肯定係搞粉個時太大力同太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ee8d91a9c4fc11d6e03b7f973f7eded9601fc3","tid":115054,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有第三個~記住加左粉之後就盡快搞到冇粉粒就即落模拍走大空氣就入模!!咁就7成發得起"},{"pid":"3a04cc19627263d1a7c61b9b21a46fa6bfce36d6","tid":115054,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有第三個~記住加左粉之後就盡快搞到冇粉粒就即落模拍走大空氣就入<span style=\"color: red;\">爐</span>!!咁就7成發得起</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3384b1a971da5a1e14e9a8b7f604038fea81c74d","tid":115054,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"望到第二個 我笑撚左三分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf52ba15145ef628d5dab18963e48fd01bab083","tid":115054,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"一睇就知煲燶啦<br />\n叫你放水又唔聽<br />\n一份三碗水嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21cf12012d238e95696f586a2e894c2419beb3fe","tid":115054,"uid":19194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffac830ca84382974a8f5c7ff8ae441e5c36f0c6","tid":115054,"uid":19879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"我都想整蛋糕送比男朋友<br />\n但我都係地獄廚神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實男仔鐘意收出面買既朱古力<br />\n定係親手整既野食"},{"pid":"5cce835e306819a472c55b332975e2d5e6c7c8f3","tid":115054,"uid":71733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"如果你想個蛋糕邊邊位焗出黎靚d,就沿住周圍掃一層牛油，再灑一層朱古力粉，原理就好似心太軟咁，保持返個形狀<br />\n<br />\n如果你想焗得表面平均d，包一層錫紙，再隔水焗，熱力會平均分布。你個蛋糕模當然要係有底"},{"pid":"4eb6fa766bc4ddc629d6cf6236cc09fc7826eebd","tid":115054,"uid":56594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a057a8855a75adde0ec280a791f2f199acb03f","tid":115054,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:18:26.000Z","msg":"所以咪有忌廉外層做掩飾，或者索性整碎個蛋糕做餡"},{"pid":"66643e2c264bdb7699cedc3048a1820f58cdbca0","tid":115054,"uid":64469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:27:27.000Z","msg":"絲打我撐你<br />\n第一眼望到即刻諗起朱古力陣甜味，好想試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加油啦整多幾次就會似樣架啦個蛋糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fbc5fe656b1c2fb192bc986bfe77feef3578e39","tid":115054,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1o9hcb7p\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1o9hcb7p&h=3b2e3873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7db0453ecf2f60adbef2de43fcc39b0c7992b94","tid":115054,"uid":12861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"突然拉到樓主ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a5fa66f534bb123aa456fa3c3a7c32d5296746","tid":115054,"uid":42009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T15:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你想個蛋糕邊邊位焗出黎靚d,就沿住周圍掃一層牛油，再灑一層朱古力粉，原理就好似心太軟咁，保持返個形狀<br />\n<br />\n如果你想焗得表面平均d，包一層錫紙，再隔水焗，熱力會平均分布。你個蛋糕模當然要係有底</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加油絲打！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a7585e52772bd55ea2961a86e62496f3f6966b","tid":115054,"uid":50591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"另類自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b43eaec217ec9336c377392651e3fadb6ad9ea8","tid":115054,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"咩事 變自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 幾大波"},{"pid":"496a13258619f71f419ec69135ad5aa7bb5acdd3","tid":115054,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T16:10:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另類自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自咩爆 高登時代k